items.name: Glory Destiny Wiki
items.title: Glory Destiny Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Glory Destiny Wikia!
items.desc: Glory Destiny, (also known as Spirit Tales, 晴空物语) is a free to play, MMORPG created by X-Legend and published by Koramgame. The name is often stylized as 【Glory Destiny】Online (【晴空物语】马来西亚中文版) or <Glory Destiny Online>. This game comes in two different, playable languages: English and Traditional Chinese.

items.name: Destiny Wiki
items.title: Destiny Wiki
items.headline: Seeing you starside..
items.desc: Destiny Wiki is a fan-created and fan-administered Wiki devoted to providing the most complete, accurate, and up-to-date information about ''Destiny'', the upcoming shared-world first-person shooter game from Bungie (the creators of ''Halo'') and published by Activision.  Destiny Wiki is the best source for information on Destiny's story, universe, gameplay features, characters, missions, and items.

items.name: Wings of destiny Wiki
items.title: Wings of destiny Wiki
items.headline: Wings of Destiny Wikia
items.desc: Welcome to the Wings of Destiny Wikia! This wikia is dedicated to providing information about the game called Wings of Destiny. Wings of Destiny (WoD) is a web-based Massively Multiplayer Online Role-Playing Game (MMORPG) that people can play by signing in with an account through Facebook or the IGG website. The game was released in September 2012 and is a 3D-based game. Enter now to learn more!

items.name: Destinypedia
items.title: Destinypedia
items.headline: Destinypedia - ¡Sigue tu Destino!
items.desc:
La Destinypedia es el wiki dedicado a la nueva franquicia de videojuegos llamada "Destiny", un nuevo universo situado 700 años en el futuro en el que los humanos han perdido todo y solo les queda una única ciudad en la Tierra. 

Alucinantes mundos para explorar nos esperan de la mano de Bungie Studios, los creadores de Halo, y de la distribuidora Activision.
